seriesStmt.title: Gregor Joseph Werner: A thematic catalogue of his works

annot.p: While the A-HE source is attributed to Werner, the A-Ed source quotes Antonio Caldara as author. Given the compositional technique of the work, the latter attribution is more likely.
After this movement, parts contain a directive Fiat Toccato si placet or similar.
